        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Looking to upgrade your space with beautiful and bold furniture? Explore our handpicked collection of wooden and engineered wood furniture made for modern homes and busy offices. From wooden shoe racks to compact cabinets and spacious wardrobes, we have everything you need to stay organized in style.</p><p>Are you a new Furniva customer in need of a stylish shoe organizer? Look no more - our wooden shoe racks offer sleek solutions to keep your footwear in place while adding charm to your hallway or even bedroom.</p><p>Planning a bedroom makeover or bookroom? Choose from our range of engineered wood cabinets - perfect for books, crockery, files, or everyday essentials.</p><p>Our furniture is crafted from premium engineered wood, ensuring quality as well as durability without compromising on style. We offer multiple finishes and sizes - from bold geometric patterns to aesthetic yet simple pieces to suit all types of apartments or a spacious villa.</p><p>So whether you're furnishing a new home or just adding that perfect cabinet or shoe rack, browse our range today. Your perfect piece is just a click away.</p>"
